T02TD1960E:92a-1: krishna ya m'a ri n'a ma s'a dha na /
T02TD1960E:92a-3: gshin rje dgra nag po zhes bya ba'i sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02TD1960E:92a-4: dpal zhe sdang gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1960E:92a-5: bla ma la gus phyag 'tshal nas //
T02TD1960E:92a-6: de rjes gshin dgra nag rdor la //
T02TD1960E:92a-7: rang 'od yan lag bzhugs pa yi //

T02TD1960E:92a-9: rdo rje ral gri 'khor lo dang //
T02TD1960E:92a-12: de la phyag 'tshal sgrub thabs bri //
T02TD1960E:92a-13: gshin dgra nag po'i sgrub thabs 'di //

T02TD1960E:92a-17: byis pa rnams kyis go bde dang //

T02TD1960E:92a-25: thog mar gdong sogs dag byas nas //
T02TD1960E:92a-26: snga dro gshin rje bdag gnyid pas //
T02TD1960E:92a-27: dben yul la ni rab tu brtsam //
T02TD1960E:92b-0: dur khrod la sogs bde @92b stan bzhugs //
T02TD1960E:92b-1: rang snying padma'i zla ba la //

T02TD1960E:92b-30: blo ldan de rnams gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1960E:92b-31: snying rje'i rim pa mthong nas ni //
T02TD1960E:92b-32: sna tshogs stong par rnam dmigs na //

T02TD1960E:92b-35: rnam par rtog pa med pa'i phyir //

T02TD1960E:92b-37: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /

T02TD1960E:92b-42: bsrung ba'i don du rdo rje bsgom //

T02TD1960E:92b-44: rdo rje sa gzhi de las byung //

T02TD1960E:92b-49: rtag rdor yan lag las byung ngo //
T02TD1960E:92b-50: dkar po gru gsum chos dbyings te //

T02TD1960E:93a-2: dag pa'i yan lag las byung ste //

T02TD1960E:93a-12: lho ru ser po yang dag ldan //
T02TD1960E:93a-13: nub kyi cha ni dmar po yin //
T02TD1960E:93a-14: byang du ljang gu'i kha dog go //
T02TD1960E:93a-16: dbus kyis ni rnam bsgoms te //
T02TD1960E:93a-17: 'di ltar phyogs kyi dbye ba yis //
T02TD1960E:93a-18: sna tshogs rdo rje bsgom bya'o //
T02TD1960E:93a-19: bris sku la yang de bzhin bsgom //
T02TD1960E:93a-20: rab tu gzugs kyi rim ji bzhin //
T02TD1960E:93a-21: rnam lnga bsam par byas nas ni //
T02TD1960E:93a-22: sangs rgyas gzugs brnyan rnam bsgom mo //
T02TD1960E:93a-23: rnam lnga de ni dpal dang ldan //
T02TD1960E:93a-24: de rjes gang bar bdud sel byed //
T02TD1960E:93a-25: de ni sangs rgyas gzugs brnyan grags //
T02TD1960E:93a-26: de phyir de la de gsungs so //
T02TD1960E:93a-27: lte bar sna tshogs pad zla la //
T02TD1960E:93a-28: dbyangs yig nyis skor dgod par bya //
T02TD1960E:93a-29: de yis zla ba rdzogs pa ste //
T02TD1960E:93a-30: ka yi thog mar nyis skor bya //
T02TD1960E:93a-31: da dha da dha ya la drug / bsnan pas de rnams rdzogs pa yis //
T02TD1960E:93a-32: zla ba dmar po rnam bsgom bya //
T02TD1960E:93a-33: de gnyis rdzogs la ji skad gsungs //
T02TD1960E:93a-34: me long mnyam pa nyid du brjod //
T02TD1960E:93a-35: de dbus h'um skyes so sor rtog / de las gyur pa rdo rje ste //
T02TD1960E:93a-36: de ni bya ba nan tan brjod //
T02TD1960E:93a-37: nyi ma'i nor bu 'od zer mtshungs //
T02TD1960E:93a-38: 'od dang sa bon lan rdo rje //
T02TD1960E:93a-40: zhes bya bas nga rgyal bya'o //
T02TD1960E:93a-41: de la skyes pa kha dog dkar //
T02TD1960E:93a-42: thub pa'i mchog gis rab brgyan pa //
T02TD1960E:93a-44: sgeg pa khro bo'i gzugs can no //
T02TD1960E:93a-45: mchog gi bde ba dang ldan pa //
T02TD1960E:93a-46: dkar po sngon po dmar po'i zhal //
T02TD1960E:93a-47: g-yas bskum g-yon brkyang bar gnas pa //
T02TD1960E:93a-48: 'bar ba dang ldan ral gri dang //
T02TD1960E:93a-49: rdo rje gri gug gsor bar byed //
T02TD1960E:93a-51: g-yas pa'i g-yon du shin tu yang //
T02TD1960E:93a-53: aom dharma dh'a tu dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1960E:93a-54: zhes bya bas rnam pa lnga'i rang bzhin las //
T02TD1960E:93b-0: chags pa che @93b bas 'dul ba yis //
T02TD1960E:93b-1: 'gro ba gsum ni kun du dmigs //
T02TD1960E:93b-2: rang gi rnam shes 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1960E:93b-3: sna tshogs spros pa rdzogs sangs rgyas //
T02TD1960E:93b-4: rtag bde dga' ba'i rang bzhin can //

T02TD1960E:93b-14: 'khor lo'i bdag po skul byed do //

T02TD1960E:93b-19: 'jig rten mgron gnyer stong bar bzhugs //
T02TD1960E:93b-20: 'jig rten bsod nams rje btsun bzhengs //
T02TD1960E:93b-21: kye stong par bsams nas ci ste bzhugs //
T02TD1960E:93b-22: byang chub rang bzhin 'jig rten mgron //

T02TD1960E:93b-24: chags pa'i rjes chags thim pa'o //

T02TD1960E:93b-26: 'od du zhu ba'i bde sems ni //
T02TD1960E:93b-27: rab tu zhu zhing zhu la skyes //
T02TD1960E:93b-28: nyi dkyil la ni ya sngon te //
T02TD1960E:93b-29: khro bo dang ni khros pa can //
T02TD1960E:93b-30: rus pa'i rgyan gyis yang dag brgyan //
T02TD1960E:93b-31: smin ma rnon po 'bar ba can //
T02TD1960E:93b-32: yan lag spu gri bzhin 'jigs sbyin //
T02TD1960E:93b-33: rdo rje sngon po 'od dang ldan //

T02TD1960E:93b-36: nag po dgra yi gzugs byas nas //
T02TD1960E:93b-38: sna tshogs bdag nyid mnyam par bzhugs //
T02TD1960E:93b-39: ma he'i rdo rje bsams nas ni //
T02TD1960E:93b-40: dkyil 'khor bdag po rnam par bsgoms //
T02TD1960E:93b-41: dug bzhin tsha ba 'phros pa ni //
T02TD1960E:93b-43: mun nag lus ni drag shul can //
T02TD1960E:93b-46: smin ma sma ra skra gyen te //
T02TD1960E:93b-47: g-yas bskum g-yon brkyang zhabs kyis gnas //
T02TD1960E:93b-48: dus ni mi dran byed pa'o //
T02TD1960E:93b-49: rtsa ba'i zhal ni bung ba che //
T02TD1960E:93b-50: g-yas pa shin tu zla ba 'od //
T02TD1960E:93b-51: g-yon pa dmar po rab tu gsungs //

T02TD1960E:94a-0: mi thung gsus chen nag po @94a * //

T02TD1960E:94a-16: rigs ldan ser pos dpung rgyan te//

T02TD1960E:94a-28: mche gnyis so phreng lce gnyis pa'o //

T02TD1960E:94a-34: zhes bya ba 'dis ni rjes su rnal 'byor ro //
T02TD1960E:94a-35: rang snying 'od zer lcags kyus dgug / mkha' khyab rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun //
T02TD1960E:94a-36: thams cad de ni zhal du gzhug / bde zhugs 'bab cing snying gar zhu //
T02TD1960E:94a-37: byas pas blo ldan rnal 'byor gyis //

T02TD1960E:94a-40: sa bon gzugs kyis dmigs par bya //
T02TD1960E:94a-42: sa bon rnams kyi byin rlabs te //

T02TD1960E:94a-45: gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid ji bzhin pa ;

T02TD1960E:95a-36: nub kyi sna tshogs pad nyi la //
T02TD1960E:95a-37: rim pas de ni rnam bsgom bya //
T02TD1960E:95a-38: pra dzny'a dhrik ni de nyid kyis //
T02TD1960E:95a-39: phrag dog dgra ni rnam zil byed //
T02TD1960E:95a-40: byang gi padmo rnon po la //
T02TD1960E:95a-41: de ni rim pas gnas par bsam //
T02TD1960E:95a-42: mung+gar dhrik ni de nyid kyis //
T02TD1960E:95a-43: shar phyogs sgo ru padma la //
T02TD1960E:95a-44: nyi dkyil la ni 'bar zhing gnas //
T02TD1960E:95a-45: tho ba mthar byed min zhes bya //
T02TD1960E:95a-46: rim pas mkhas pas yang dag bsam //
T02TD1960E:95a-47: danda dhrik ces bya sngags kyis ;
T02TD1960E:95a-48: / lho yi sgo ru yang dag gnas //
T02TD1960E:95a-49: be con gshin dgra mi bgrungs pa //
T02TD1960E:95a-50: sna tshogs pad nyi zla 'od bsam //
T02TD1960E:95a-51: padma dhrik ces bya bas ni //
T02TD1960E:95a-52: padma dus med gshin dgra ste //
T02TD1960E:95a-53: nub sgor 'dam skyes nyi dkyil la //
T02TD1960E:95a-54: 'khrugs pa stobs chen bsam par bya //
T02TD1960E:95b-0: khadga dhrik ni de nyid @95b kyis ;
T02TD1960E:95b-1: / ral gri de ni dus med pa //
T02TD1960E:95b-2: sna tshogs pad dang nyi dkyil la //
T02TD1960E:95b-3: bdud med byed pa byang sgor sgom //
T02TD1960E:95b-4: sna tshogs rdo rje grva bzhi ru //
T02TD1960E:95b-5: gzhan yang de bzhin lha mo bsam //
T02TD1960E:95b-6: dve sha ra ti zhes sngags kyis //
T02TD1960E:95b-7: shar lho mtshams kyi lha mo ste //
T02TD1960E:95b-8: zla ba dang ni sna tshogs pad //
T02TD1960E:95b-9: khros ma ts'a rtsi yang dag gnas //
T02TD1960E:95b-10: de nas lho nub rdo rje phag / rigs kyi bdag mo phag mo ste //
T02TD1960E:95b-11: mo ha ra ti de nyid kyis //
T02TD1960E:95b-12: padma zla bar mkhas pas bsgom //
T02TD1960E:95b-13: de nas nub byang grva nyid la //
T02TD1960E:95b-14: r'a ga ra ti zhes sngags kyis //
T02TD1960E:95b-15: pad zla la ni dbyangs can dgod //
T02TD1960E:95b-16: de nas byang shar dkar mo ste //
T02TD1960E:95b-17: badzra ra ti zhes sngags kyis //
T02TD1960E:95b-18: zla pad la ni lha mo bsgom //
T02TD1960E:95b-19: dkyil 'khor gyi ni grva bzhi ru //
T02TD1960E:95b-20: de nyid gsum gyi bhandha rnams //
T02TD1960E:95b-22: dam par byas na bde dang ldan //
T02TD1960E:95b-23: gong ma'i 'khor lo de thim ste //
T02TD1960E:95b-24: mnyam nyid pas ni dmigs pa ste //
T02TD1960E:95b-26: gshin dgra nag po dus 'jigs pas //
T02TD1960E:95b-27: de yi rang bzhin dkyil lha rnams //
T02TD1960E:95b-28: mig dang lus sogs rang bzhin te //
T02TD1960E:95b-29: lha rnams kyis ni byin rlabs bya //
T02TD1960E:95b-30: gtu mug kshim la 'khor lo skyes //
T02TD1960E:95b-31: cung zhig khros pa'i mig la gnas //
T02TD1960E:95b-32: rdo rje mig yin blo ldan dmigs //
T02TD1960E:95b-33: rna gnyis dzri las rdo rje byung //
T02TD1960E:95b-34: rdo rje rna ba kha dog gnag / dri las kham skyes rin chen 'byung //
T02TD1960E:95b-35: ser sna de ni zla ba la //
T02TD1960E:95b-36: rdo rje dri ni de bzhin mchog / ljags la gam las padma byung //
T02TD1960E:95b-37: 'dod chags dra ba rdor ljags yin //
T02TD1960E:95b-38: kam las skyes pa ral gri ste //
T02TD1960E:95b-39: ri dags mtshan pa'i rdor lus yin //
T02TD1960E:95b-40: phrag dog gshin dgra rang bzhin gzugs //
T02TD1960E:95b-41: dpral bar lus yin zhes bya ste //
T02TD1960E:95b-42: lte stengs sam las rdo rje yin //
T02TD1960E:95b-43: rdo rje sems ni de bzhin mchog / sgeg po khro bo rang bzhin gzugs //
T02TD1960E:95b-44: rdo rje 'dzin pa dgod bya ste //
T02TD1960E:95b-45: 'di ni yan lag drug dgod pa'o //
T02TD1960E:95b-46: mngon sum don grub las su gsungs //
T02TD1960E:95b-47: snying gar h'um rdor dbus su gnas //
T02TD1960E:95b-48: h'um rdor sngon po legs 'od can //
T02TD1960E:95b-49: gshin dgra dang 'dra phyag mtshan mtshungs //
T02TD1960E:95b-50: sems la gnas pa'i thugs rdor bsgom //
T02TD1960E:95b-51: ao la gong aa las padma skyes //
T02TD1960E:95b-52: de dbus pum las chags pa byung //
T02TD1960E:95b-53: 'dod chags gshin dgra lta bu'i lus //
T02TD1960E:96a-2: spyi bor aom rnams 'khor lo dbus //
T02TD1960E:96a-4: sku yi rdo rje sku dang 'dra //
T02TD1960E:96a-5: phyag dang phyag mtshan kha dog mtshungs //
T02TD1960E:96a-6: de ni de nyid rdor mchog ste //
T02TD1960E:96a-7: rdzogs pas mkha' gnas sangs rgyas mchod //
T02TD1960E:96a-8: sngags kyis de rnams byin rlabs bya //
T02TD1960E:96a-9: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta tsitta badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1960E:96a-10: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta w'a ka badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1960E:96a-11: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta k'a ya badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1960E:96a-12: rang snying sa bon 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1960E:96a-13: sras dang bcas pa'i sangs rgyas kun //
T02TD1960E:96a-14: sna tshogs la gnas dgug byas pas //
T02TD1960E:96a-15: mdun du de ni bzhugs dmigs te //
T02TD1960E:96a-16: des ni yang dag spros pa yi //
T02TD1960E:96a-17: ji srid ts'a rtsi la sogs pa //
T02TD1960E:96a-18: zla 'od mtshungs pa'i bum pa yis //
T02TD1960E:96a-19: bkra shis la sogs glu rnams kyis //
T02TD1960E:96a-20: yang ni dbang bskur dmigs par bya //
T02TD1960E:96a-21: bdag nyid dang ni thams cad la //
T02TD1960E:96a-22: dbang bskur bas ni ci byung ste //
T02TD1960E:96a-23: spyi bor gshin dgra nag po yi //
T02TD1960E:96a-24: rdor 'dzin bdag nyid de bzhin no //
T02TD1960E:96a-25: rang snying sa bon 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1960E:96a-26: bdag mdun ye shes 'khor lo dgug /'khor lo de ni dmigs nas ni //
T02TD1960E:96a-27: khro rnams bgegs bskrad srung bar byed //
T02TD1960E:96a-28: aargha bsil yab phul byas nas //
T02TD1960E:96a-30: 'di sngags kyis ni dgug pa ste //
T02TD1960E:96a-32: 'di sngags kyis ni rab tu gzhug / aom padma bam /
T02TD1960E:96a-34: aom khadga ho: sngags 'di yis ni dbang byed do //
T02TD1960E:96a-35: rang snying sa bon 'od rnams kyis //
T02TD1960E:96a-36: sangs rgyas dgug cing gzhug pa ste //
T02TD1960E:96a-37: snying gar 'od zhu dmigs nas ni //
T02TD1960E:96a-38: ma lus rdo rje lam nas dbyung //
T02TD1960E:96a-40: zla ba las byung lha mo rnams //
T02TD1960E:96a-41: sna tshogs me tog la sogs rdzas //
T02TD1960E:96a-42: phyag gi yal gas de rnams 'dzin //
T02TD1960E:96a-43: sgeg ldan de yi mchod pa ste //
T02TD1960E:96a-44: yid 'phrog mchod pa'i glu dang ni //
T02TD1960E:96a-45: sna tshogs gar gyi bye brag gis //
T02TD1960E:96a-46: des ni bde chen rab yin no //
T02TD1960E:96a-47: kye kye gshin rje dgra nag po //
T02TD1960E:96a-48: bla ma srin po'i rang bzhin can //
T02TD1960E:96a-49: khyod mthong bdag ni rnam 'jigs te //
T02TD1960E:96a-50: bla ma khro bo'i rang bzhin spongs //
T02TD1960E:96a-51: bdag pos gar byed pa yis ni //
T02TD1960E:96b-0: mig sman bcag @96b bzhin khros pa'i yid //
T02TD1960E:96b-1: mig bgrungs khyod ni gar byed do //
T02TD1960E:96b-2: mi thung nag po gshin dgra ste //
T02TD1960E:96b-3: gzugs ni rnam pa sna tshogs sprul //
T02TD1960E:96b-4: rdo rje dbyangs can bdag gis zhus //
T02TD1960E:96b-5: bde chen khyod ni gar mdzod cig / hr'i: shtri: sngags kyis khyod gar byed //
T02TD1960E:96b-6: khams gsum the tshom med par mdzod //
T02TD1960E:96b-7: gshin rje khro bo rje btsun khyod //
T02TD1960E:96b-9: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta p'u dza badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1960E:96b-10: thams cad sgra brnyan lta bu'i dpe //
T02TD1960E:96b-11: sgra yul bzhin du rnam dmigs bya'o //
T02TD1960E:96b-12: 'khor lo la gnas lha rnams kyis //
T02TD1960E:96b-13: 'khor lo'i bdag po bstod pa ste//
T02TD1960E:96b-14: gti mug rdo rje rang bzhin khyod //
T02TD1960E:96b-16: sangs rgyas kun ldan mgon po ste //
T02TD1960E:96b-18: ser sna rdo rje rang bzhin khyod //
T02TD1960E:96b-19: yang dag gshin dgra 'jigs pa po //
T02TD1960E:96b-20: thugs kyi rdo rje rab snang ba //
T02TD1960E:96b-21: rin chen rdo rje phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1960E:96b-22: 'dod chags rdo rje rang bzhin khyod //
T02TD1960E:96b-23: 'dod chags rgya mtsho chos kyi bdag / thams cad dbyangs kyi mchog gi mchog / gsung gi rdo rje phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1960E:96b-24: phrag dog rdo rje rang bzhin khyod //
T02TD1960E:96b-25: gshin dgra las kun thams cad byed //
T02TD1960E:96b-26: sku yi rdo rje rab snang ba //
T02TD1960E:96b-27: ral gri phyag la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1960E:96b-28: sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin khyod //
T02TD1960E:96b-29: sangs rgyas kun gcig yang dag 'dus //
T02TD1960E:96b-30: sangs rgyas thams cad mchog gi mchog / dkyil 'khor mnga' bdag phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1960E:96b-31: aa las skyes pa'i dag pad de //
T02TD1960E:96b-32: mgo gsum steng du yang dag gnas //
T02TD1960E:96b-34: gru gsum ram ba las byung ba'o //
T02TD1960E:96b-36: g-yo ba sngon po gzhu dang 'dra //
T02TD1960E:96b-37: yam las skyes pa ba dan dang //
T02TD1960E:96b-38: de la kha dog ming dang gzugs //
T02TD1960E:96b-39: snang mdzad la sogs gnas pa ste //
T02TD1960E:96b-40: de la sogs pa yang dag dbyung //
T02TD1960E:96b-41: rigs ngan la sogs rnam pa lnga //
T02TD1960E:96b-42: h'um las rdo rje rim pa yis //
T02TD1960E:96b-43: de ni dgag pa bsgom par bya //
T02TD1960E:96b-44: rlung gis me ni rab sbar pas //
T02TD1960E:96b-45: zhu bzhin rnam par dmigs pa yin //
T02TD1960E:96b-46: rdo rje ro mnyam bsgyur ba ste //
T02TD1960E:96b-47: gshin dgra dri med dmigs pa'o //
T02TD1960E:97a-2: sangs rgyas ye shes rang bzhin dgug / sngags kyi gzugs kyis rab tu gzhug / dmigs nas bdud rtsi lnga mchog ste //
T02TD1960E:97a-3: de nyid gsum gyis byin brlabs nas //
T02TD1960E:97a-4: dkyil 'khor bdag po tshim par bya //
T02TD1960E:97a-5: zhi ba rdo rje lci la gnas //
T02TD1960E:97a-6: h'um las skyes pa dmigs nas ni //
T02TD1960E:97a-7: de la sdu gu'i rnam pa yis //
T02TD1960E:97a-8: des ni mnyam par dgug par bya //
T02TD1960E:97a-9: sna tshogs gnas pa'i rdzogs sangs rgyas //
T02TD1960E:97a-10: dkyil 'khor lha rnams de bzhin no //
T02TD1960E:97a-11: snying ga'i 'od zer rnams kyis ni //
T02TD1960E:97a-12: rnam rtog spangs pas dmigs bya'o //
T02TD1960E:97a-13: thog ma dbus mtha' dbye ba yis //
T02TD1960E:97a-14: 'di la gcig tu sbyor med de //
T02TD1960E:97a-15: rdul phran cha med rgyu yin pas //
T02TD1960E:97a-16: grangs med de ni sbyor mi bya //
T02TD1960E:97a-17: gcig dang du ma'i rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD1960E:97a-18: rnam par bral ba gang yin de //
T02TD1960E:97a-19: de ni de bzhin de ma yin //
T02TD1960E:97a-20: the tshom de nyid las bya'o //
T02TD1960E:97a-21: gang phyir the tshom gnyis la gnas //
T02TD1960E:97a-22: bsam mi khyab la the tshom med //
T02TD1960E:97a-23: spro dang bsdu ba'i sku yin te //
T02TD1960E:97a-24: sems can ro gcig don las byung //
T02TD1960E:97a-25: gzhan ni rgyas par de nyid med //
T02TD1960E:97a-26: 'di ni gsal bar rab tu gsungs //
T02TD1960E:97a-27: ye shes zhabs kyi zhal nas byung //
T02TD1960E:97a-28: dpal ldan gsang ba 'dus par gsungs //
T02TD1960E:97a-29: 'di la bdag gis rgyas ma smras //
T02TD1960E:97a-30: dngos po'i bdag nyid dngos po med //
T02TD1960E:97a-31: khams med rnam par shes pa'ang med //
T02TD1960E:97a-32: nam mkha' kun mnyam gnas bzhin te //
T02TD1960E:97a-33: nam mkha' ji bzhin bdag med pa //
T02TD1960E:97a-34: 'di ni chos mchog bde chen po //
T02TD1960E:97a-35: sa min chu min gnyi ga min ;
T02TD1960E:97a-36: / me min rlung min mkha' min te //
T02TD1960E:97a-37: rdo rje sems dpa' rab sbyor bas //
T02TD1960E:97a-38: skye ba 'di ni rab gnas pa'i //
T02TD1960E:97a-39: dngos po thams cad dngos min te //
T02TD1960E:97a-40: de'i phyir dngos med grags pa'o //
T02TD1960E:97a-42: rtag dang chad pa gnyis min te //
T02TD1960E:97a-43: zhal med phyag med kha dog med //
T02TD1960E:97a-44: mchog gi dga' ba'i mtshan nyid la //
T02TD1960E:97a-45: dngos po thams cad nges rtag min //
T02TD1960E:97a-46: thog ma dbus mtha' rnam par spangs //
T02TD1960E:97a-47: de ltar pho brang shes gnas pas //
T02TD1960E:97a-48: rnam rtog thams cad spangs pa ste //
T02TD1960E:97a-49: phung po khams dang bdag med par //
T02TD1960E:97b-0: dag @97b pa'i bde gzugs bsgom pa'o //
T02TD1960E:97b-1: 'gro ba gshin rje gshed byas nas //
T02TD1960E:97b-2: rang snying sa bon 'od rnams kyis //
T02TD1960E:97b-3: de bkug 'ong bar dmigs nas ni //
T02TD1960E:97b-4: sku gsung thugs rdor rang bzhin can //
T02TD1960E:97b-5: rdo rje'i rang bzhin chos yin te //
T02TD1960E:97b-6: ye shes las skyes dgod par bya //
T02TD1960E:97b-7: de la de yis bon rnams //
T02TD1960E:97b-8: hr'i: shtri: la sogs ye shes 'bar //
T02TD1960E:97b-9: lhag rtog spangs pas mthong ba ste //
T02TD1960E:97b-10: dag pa'i bde ba'i rnam pa can //
T02TD1960E:97b-12: bdag nyid mkhas pas bsgom pa yin //
T02TD1960E:97b-13: sku la sogs par 'phro bya ste //
T02TD1960E:97b-14: dus gcig dang ni rim pa yis ;
T02TD1960E:97b-15: / khro gzugs sna tshogs sprul pa byed //
T02TD1960E:97b-16: hr'i: shtri: la sogs sngags kyis ni //
T02TD1960E:97b-17: 'gro ba thams cad bde byed do //
T02TD1960E:97b-18: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1960E:97b-19: bsam gtan byed pa'i rim pa 'dis //
T02TD1960E:97b-20: 'bad la sngags ni de bzhin bya //
T02TD1960E:97b-21: gzhan yang bza' ba la sogs las //
T02TD1960E:97b-22: bsam gtan ldan zhing thams cad bya'o //
T02TD1960E:97b-23: mchod dang bstod dang bdud rtsi za //
T02TD1960E:97b-24: sems can don byed yid kyis bya //
T02TD1960E:97b-25: de nyid gsum gyi rim pa yis //
T02TD1960E:97b-26: ye shes 'khor lo rnam par dbyung //
T02TD1960E:97b-27: bdag gi 'khor lo bdag nyid la //
T02TD1960E:97b-28: ji ltar rim pas gnas pa ste //
T02TD1960E:97b-29: bdag gis bsod nams byas pa gang //
T02TD1960E:97b-30: mngon par byang chub la smon bya //
T02TD1960E:97b-31: de nas smon lam byas nas ni //
T02TD1960E:97b-32: aom a'a: h'um mu:'i sngags kyis ni //
T02TD1960E:97b-33: ye shes 'khor lo gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1960E:97b-35: rang bdag rnam pa'i rang bzhin bzhengs //
T02TD1960E:97b-36: de yi nga rgyal yang dag byed //
T02TD1960E:97b-37: 'bad la dngos po thams cad ni //
T02TD1960E:97b-38: de bzhin de yi gzugs nges bya //
T02TD1960E:97b-39: gti mug gshin dgra'i gzugs kyis ni //
T02TD1960E:97b-41: gsungs pa'i dus ni de rnams la //
T02TD1960E:97b-44: cung zhig ye shes de rjes sbyor //
T02TD1960E:97b-45: sbyor bdag yang dag rnal 'byor che //
T02TD1960E:97b-46: yang dag ye shes dbang gnas so //
T02TD1960E:97b-47: ji ltar gsungs pa'i rim pa gcig / dus gcig la ni sngags bsgom bya //
T02TD1960E:98a-3: de nyid ye shes gzugs can dag / de phyir bdag nyid gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1960E:98a-4: dbang bskur rim pa bsam gtan gyis //
T02TD1960E:98a-5: khrus dang bza' ba thams cad bya //
T02TD1960E:98a-6: de bzhin bdud rtsi'i rim pa yis //
T02TD1960E:98a-7: gzhan mchod pa la rtogs par bya ;
T02TD1960E:98a-8: / bdag nyid dang ni gzhan ma rnams //
T02TD1960E:98a-9: rim pa ltar ni rtag tu mchod //
T02TD1960E:98a-10: dpal ldan gshin dgra'i bdag nyid can //
T02TD1960E:98a-11: byang chub bsgom pas rtag tu dmigs //
T02TD1960E:98a-12: bdag gzhan mnyam pa byang chub yin //
T02TD1960E:98a-13: de phyir rang bdag sbyor ba ste //
T02TD1960E:98a-14: de med bdag nyid bsgyur 'dod pa //
T02TD1960E:98a-15: rnal 'byor chos sgrub pa rnyed min no //
T02TD1960E:98a-16: ji ltar sna tshogs rnam pa la //
T02TD1960E:98a-17: dngos po gcig la rtog pa ste //
T02TD1960E:98a-18: sdug bsngal bral nas bde ba skye //
T02TD1960E:98a-19: las kyi dbye bas de dag skye'o //
T02TD1960E:98a-20: bdag nyid sems la rnam rtog med //
T02TD1960E:98a-21: dag pa'i dga' ba'i rang bzhin can //
T02TD1960E:98a-22: thabs dang shes rab rang bzhin la //
T02TD1960E:98a-23: nag ces pa ni dga' ba'o //
T02TD1960E:98a-24: des ni 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho la //
T02TD1960E:98a-25: de skyes 'khril bas shi dus su //
T02TD1960E:98a-26: zab pa stobs chen gshin dgra nag / des ni phan byed gzhan min no //
T02TD1960E:98a-27: gshin sgrub zhags pa lcags kyu 'dzin //
T02TD1960E:98a-29: de rnams dgug cing phur pas gdab //
T02TD1960E:98a-30: de ni 'jigs can khro gzugs so //
T02TD1960E:98a-31: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat /
T02TD1960E:98a-32: 'byung po thams cad 'khor dang bcas pa dgug pa ste dza: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat /
T02TD1960E:98a-33: 'byung po thams cad 'khor dang bcas pa phur bus gdab pa ste h'um phat /
T02TD1960E:98a-35: rang gi kha dog brgyan pa brtag / g-yas pa'i phyag la rang mtshon 'dzin //
T02TD1960E:98a-36: g-yon pa'i phyag na sna tshogs pa'o //
T02TD1960E:98a-37: brgya byin gshin rje dbang ldan dang //
T02TD1960E:98a-38: hr'i: shtri: wi kri sa bon gyis //
T02TD1960E:98a-39: de dag thams cad rdzogs pa ste //
T02TD1960E:98a-40: me dang bden bral rlung lha dang //
T02TD1960E:98a-41: h'um byung lus ni shes bya ste //
T02TD1960E:98a-42: nyi zla sa yi 'jig rten lha //
